Package: surfaceuv
Type: Package
Title: Solar Ultraviolet at Ground Surface Data Import 
Version: 0.1.1.9000
Date: 2024-11-06
Authors@R:
   c(
    person("Pedro J.", "Aphalo", email = "pedro.aphalo@helsinki.fi", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3385-972X"))
    )
Description: Functions for reading files containing data on "Surface UV" such 
    as daily doses, irradiances and the UV Index (UVI). Currently the Surface
    UV product from the AC SAF project of EUMETSAT is supported in both
    geographic grid (HDF5) and time series (text) formats. Additionally the
    OMI/Aura Surface UV product files in geographic grid NetCDF4 and HDF5 
    formats is supported.
